content: This is an ice sculpture OF a frozen spider web, not an actual frozen spider web.
Never in a million years thought I would say a spider web is pretty. I'd think its real.
Bit of a bummer for the spider.
I had spiders, but this web is amazing

How can something so ugly, hairy and potentially dangerous, be so beautiful!
Just don't bring it any closer to me!! Thanks!!, (HELP!!)
